        <p class="page__text">
            Setting up your avatar and personalizing your nickname on Binance is
            quick and easy. Users can go to binance.com under Dashboard >
            Settings > My Profile > Avatar and Nickname. For those of you who
            own NFT assets, you can select the NFT you want to use from your
            collection as your avatar to personalize your profile. For users who
            do not own any NFT avatars, check out the NFT avatar collections
            page to get started.
        </p>
        <p class="page__text">
